{"type":null,"faqId":43957,"title":"如何节省手机流量","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body62419562\"><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__ul9860484\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__li24905153\">有 WLAN 时，建议优先使用 WLAN。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__li22819790\">不使用移动数据业务时，请关闭数据业务。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__li4051522\">浏览网页时，若不需要显示网页上的图片，可以选择屏蔽网页图片。</li></ul><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__p21635497\">在“浏览器”界面，打开“菜单&gt;设置&gt;无图模式”（EMUI 4.0在“选项菜单&gt;无图模式”），打开“无图模式”即可。</p><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__p60501746\">注意：不同浏览器的操作方式有所不同，请以实际使用为准。</p><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__ul7644810\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__li36463702\">退出不使用的应用程序。</li></ul><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__p1694433\">打开最近使用的应用程序列表，按住需要退出后台的应用向上滑动来关闭该应用程序。 </p><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__ul15249905\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__li59737867\">禁止应用程序在后台通过移动网络上网。</li></ul><p class=\"msonormal\" id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0033857368__p3031417\">进入“设置&gt;应用联网”（EMUI 4.0在”手机管家&gt;流量管理&gt;应用联网”），选择要限制上网权限的应用程序，关闭对应的数据业务开关。</p></div><div></div></body>","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":1,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0033857368","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399730000,"seriesProductName":"ALE-CL00,ALE-TL00,ALE-UL00,ATH-CL00,ATH-TL00,ATH-TL00H,ATH-UL00,CRR-CL00,CRR-CL10,CRR-CL20,CRR-CL20a,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL00,CRR-UL10,CRR-UL20,CRR-UL20a,GRA-CL00,GRA-CL10,GRA-L03,GRA-L09,GRA-TL00,GRA-UL00,GRA-UL10,Jazz-CL00,Jazz-TL00,Jazz-TL10,Jazz-TL10A,Jazz-TL20,Jazz-UL00,KIW-AL10,KIW-CL00,KIW-TL00,KIW-TL00H,KIW-UL00,PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-TL11H,PLK-UL00,RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,Sophia-L00,Sophia-L05,Sophia-L07,Sophia-L09","visitedTimes":80,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"节省手机流量,数据业务上网,耗费流量","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}